Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,（和当了A片演员的朋友再会）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.36,0:00:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,（疯狂内射）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,（新井莉玛）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.73,0:00:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,－等很久了吧 －等了一下下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,－真可爱啊 －谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.89,0:00:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,将近十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:00:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还没到十年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多就那么久了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,大概有十年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,将近十年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,变化好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,－变好多 －我没变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉有点可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,超棒的啦 先让我冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,太刺激了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.57,0:01:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是说我都知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,－好像是 －想装个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,笑死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有点不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你越来越像都会女子了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.94,0:01:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微站一下试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,AV女优
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,小声一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,前女友当AV女优也挺稀罕的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.33,0:02:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的作品全看过一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,全部的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,看的很仔细哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,AV里经常见到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是这个吗 就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,教我一下是怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,想死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,－你看了很多啊 －我看了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是女演员拿着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔会有的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但那是一个人 你见过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人这样说话走路的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那是苜秀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,要采访我就做了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:02:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉非常奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在我心里是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,－真名 －是真名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,原本的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我最近看到的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是说你对那种印象比较深
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是挺深刻的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,什么第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,－就是 －是指分手之後的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,－见面 －第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,想说不会再见根本没机会见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不过和我是同一个乡下的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所以还是想见的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,总感觉有点不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,很有青梅竹马的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,当时交往的时候我是初恋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,－是第一次哦 －对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次交到女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没怎么说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 我记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我在说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,明明就说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,水晶灯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,－好漂亮啊 －超级漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,要是发光就更棒了\N还没到时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是时间的问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,才刚装好应该是在设定中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以问个奇怪的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,今天你不用工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,今天没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便问一下明天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,明天有安排了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,後天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是叫片场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不是片场啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不太淯楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我也下知道在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,开车去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他有车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,很强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,租车的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,把太衣展开给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,下面黑的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,配合真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我问一下在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,大约五公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,大概五公尺左右
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,今天和我见面只有自己讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我是新井莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,应该有人觉得似会相识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我和青梅竹马 见了面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,令人惊讶的是 事实确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没法收场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那种感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,突然就害羞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,私底下做会紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不搞得像工作一样就没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那就随便逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以直接问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候开始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,当了几年了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,第四年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,加入AV的契机是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是想做节目制作之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,比如电视
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我想着不是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,当时我还在读大学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉没什么事可做了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我想自己可以做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就想到AV
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,其实怎样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我就想知道这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,－就是感兴趣 －感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 这样其实幕後人员也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但之所以没这么做 是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有点想试试运气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,自己到底是不是值得出道的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:08:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底是处於什么位置呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,－就是 －说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,－能不能出道之类的 －对对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说自己有什么价值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不过还是想稍微了解一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那个做爱的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们 不是还没做过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,－那个时候还是处女吧 －嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了维基百科
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次是十九岁那年是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,大概18 19岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,AV女优叫新井莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就受到了很大的冲擎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来 你什么时候发现的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,听人说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,－只是碰巧 －碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就是碰巧聊到这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,羡等等是前女友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就不好玩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我一个人觉得好玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只有亲亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,而且还是法式热吻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,AV女优不是要拍片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,除了拍片也常做爱是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话 一半一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,－私底下不做吗 －我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,为甚么要小声地说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有点意思就是了 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候的事你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是那种在外面到处乱跑类型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就像那样 变化的的方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,－硬要说的话 就是比较朴素 －嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,当时没有做过 就不会再想做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,再试一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,风有点大看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才用色色的眼神看了她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有男朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是怕路上巧遇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:11:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,休假的时候只跟女生碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一瞬闲看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,瞬间看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,很高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在乡下经常看到夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,以前骑车回家在夕阳下拍过照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,记得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候穿的是校服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,牵牵手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,才不牵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不牵吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,想牵牵手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,－什么呀 －好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕有点紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,心里七上川下的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,为了再见乾一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天看了维基百科
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,评语是很辣的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,辣妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,本来不是辣妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是阴沉的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,被当成辣妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对了我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真的超适合你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什么很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会大声说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,超色的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,很色情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到你是这么色的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜欢色情的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我突然想到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要是讨厌希望你能告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那是喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好色之徒这很平常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,作为生物来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么那个时候没有做爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我是很想做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,阿 当时吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是没有勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩子的部分 比较少接触到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说的话 就不太现实了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,像是这个情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,大概就是这个原因没有做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有约的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,当时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,－现在? －要约吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,鼓起勇气了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去酒店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:15:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我想了又想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,先在这里做点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那之後就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,－不想就这样回去 －嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这间就好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就这闲吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,（欢迎光临）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,（谢谢您的光临）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,－说的是 502对吧 －对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,－好宽敞 －什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,宽敞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:16:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我有种很奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,－斗了之後有种奇怪的感觉 －什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,外套脱下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,外套脱下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我先去那里坐了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉超级尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就是很尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我选的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是你说没做过爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,－我没时间了 －怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好羞耻阿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,坐上来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,坐上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,－上去吗 －这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗 坐上去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好不妙阿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这个距离好近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,－太近了 －好近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 你不是很习惯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很近完全贴在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,心跳很快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想传达 很激动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,－你能感觉吧 －好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可以亲你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,还要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,非常柔软呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么说很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我没说话呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没说话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是被你一说 突然就害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,－不想喔 －不想说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好冰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.97,0:22:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很色吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.82,0:22:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,－可以拍吗\N－你不是已经拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.86,0:22:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要脱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.85,0:22:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,看着真大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.30,0:22:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,想拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你不讨厌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,亲一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴唇好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.99,0:23:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你躺下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,做个纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.84,0:23:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,放着就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.96,0:23:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,想看看里面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.12,0:23:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:23:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,想看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,－可以喔 －脱下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.37,0:24:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这样拍很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.75,0:24:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.00,0:24:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,－可以帮我吗 －为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.03,0:24:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.01,0:24:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道阿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.03,0:24:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,从亲吻开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.89,0:25:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.70,0:25:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,－舒服吗 －好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.20,0:25:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.61,0:26:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,欸不要拍
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.88,0:26:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.16,0:26:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不要躲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.80,0:26:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么穿着这么色的内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.88,0:26:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我超想看的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.78,0:27:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,为啥有点生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.58,0:27:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,当然要生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.97,0:27:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.23,0:27:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,拍了就和工作一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.51,0:27:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不是一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.33,0:27:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.90,0:27:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.99,0:27:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.22,0:27:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,交往的时候就想做了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.04,0:27:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,很想做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.63,0:28:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.80,0:28:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛要弄脚
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.59,0:29:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,都湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.98,0:29:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要讲
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.94,0:29:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,全湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.43,0:29:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你好湿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.69,0:29:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,－让你更湿一点 －讨厌阿
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.41,0:30:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.99,0:30:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,兴奋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.37,0:30:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.10,0:30:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.38,0:30:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那边不行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.99,0:30:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不能舔
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.45,0:30:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不行饶了我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.59,0:30:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.59,0:31:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,脱光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.75,0:31:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.70,0:31:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,－我帮你脱 －都脱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.07,0:31:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,都脱光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.28,0:31:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好色
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.94,0:31:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我脱光了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.99,0:31:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.67,0:31:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你又要拍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.78,0:31:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,都湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.84,0:31:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.86,0:31:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,超级湿的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.38,0:32:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.92,0:32:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想被拍
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.48,0:32:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.58,0:32:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.70,0:32:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你硬了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.99,0:32:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要戴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.34,0:32:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.91,0:33:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,拿掉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.16,0:33:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然这么硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.40,0:33:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.78,0:33:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要命
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.03,0:33:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.53,0:34:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里爽
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.03,0:34:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要拍我舔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.91,0:34:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那不要拍
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.10,0:34:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我舔
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.67,0:35:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.31,0:35:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.99,0:36:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,想射了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.23,0:36:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我想射了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.47,0:36:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.98,0:37:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.86,0:37:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.85,0:37:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.20,0:37:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.43,0:37:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我想插你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.35,0:37:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.50,0:37:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这样撑不久喔
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.79,0:38:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不能不戴套
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.73,0:38:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,什么牌子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.25,0:38:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,让你不戴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.30,0:38:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.86,0:38:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.30,0:38:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.57,0:38:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要插了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.14,0:38:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.12,0:38:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,想怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.65,0:38:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,干我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.58,0:39:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.05,0:39:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.25,0:39:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,做爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.60,0:39:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,做了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.56,0:40:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真是舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.20,0:40:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.26,0:40:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.83,0:40:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.76,0:40:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.72,0:40:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.27,0:40:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,继续干
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.30,0:41:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,爽死了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.24,0:41:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.13,0:41:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,看你这样我也想射了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.77,0:41:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.74,0:41:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.74,0:41:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.74,0:41:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.55,0:41:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.76,0:41:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.82,0:41:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.12,0:41:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.53,0:42:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好色情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.73,0:42:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.99,0:42:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不是演的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.07,0:42:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了这不是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.61,0:42:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.93,0:42:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再问了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.07,0:42:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不会再说这种话了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.41,0:42:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,忍耐住
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.25,0:42:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你忍得住
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.22,0:42:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.67,0:42:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不戴不一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.49,0:43:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.26,0:43:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.30,0:43:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.15,0:43:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.86,0:43:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.65,0:43:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.88,0:43:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.85,0:44:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜欢你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.80,0:44:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,交往的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.31,0:44:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.42,0:44:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.37,0:44:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.18,0:45:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.76,0:46:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.21,0:46:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.94,0:46:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.32,0:47:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.44,0:47:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.22,0:47:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.79,0:47:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.24,0:48:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.73,0:48:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.67,0:48:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.74,0:48:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.26,0:48:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞阿
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.01,0:48:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,看这
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.03,0:48:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看我这边
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.68,0:48:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.69,0:48:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,想射了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.95,0:48:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,要射在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.59,0:48:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要射哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.87,0:49:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.57,0:49:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子还是里面
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.66,0:49:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可以里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.68,0:49:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,别摆出那种表情
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.59,0:49:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射里面喔
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.53,0:49:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,射哪边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.93,0:49:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,射给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.66,0:49:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那边好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.89,0:49:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.71,0:49:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.28,0:50:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,忍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.25,0:50:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,爽到高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.75,0:50:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,－我高潮了 －我也射了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.96,0:50:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,－我射了 －我高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.18,0:50:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.34,0:50:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,插着一下
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.58,0:50:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我擦
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.43,0:50:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,流出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.12,0:50:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.95,0:50:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.80,0:51:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.91,0:51:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.44,0:51:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,射得比我想得多
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.25,0:51:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一直流出来
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.14,0:51:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,流很多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.46,0:51:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很多
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.95,0:51:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.55,0:51:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,把指甲弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.27,0:51:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,洗乾净就好
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.08,0:51:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次干就射在里面 是可以的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.28,0:52:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.28,0:52:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.20,0:52:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想要
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.92,0:52:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要一起洗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.07,0:52:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.21,0:52:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,－可以吗 －嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.18,0:52:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有必要那么吃惊吗 每次都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.11,0:52:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.66,0:52:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,－怎么说 －因为之前只接过吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.02,0:52:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然只接了吻 这次射里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.71,0:52:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来 洗澡没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.52,0:52:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,－没啥区别 －走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.79,0:53:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,－没事的 －可以进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.63,0:53:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,－可以啊 －等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.54,0:53:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,－可以啊 －等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.91,0:53:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.39,0:53:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.08,0:53:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.85,0:53:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.00,0:53:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.81,0:53:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,有点凉
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.24,0:53:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.72,0:53:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,边拍边干
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.10,0:53:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,跟平时不一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.12,0:53:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.81,0:53:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是拍片
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.88,0:54:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,认真还是要演一下
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.44,0:54:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,当然一般的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.39,0:54:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然会给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.31,0:54:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,会在意镜头的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.75,0:54:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,光线也会被照进去
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.72,0:54:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好地
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.60,0:54:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟是AV
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.53,0:54:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,要把情色传出去
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.42,0:54:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,－可以亲亲吗 －可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.67,0:54:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可以从後面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.90,0:54:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦 能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.60,0:54:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,－做到了 －做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.16,0:54:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有点挤
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.52,0:55:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.15,0:55:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.64,0:55:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,又有什么东西来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.19,0:55:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,出道作是在二月
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.27,0:55:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,配合太月发售\N穿着夏装在涩谷走
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.89,0:55:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,被国高中生用好奇的目光看着
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.74,0:55:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,还被路人拍了照片
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.13,0:55:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 那个是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.16,0:55:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我超讨厌的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.94,0:55:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,确实穿得很少
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.44,0:55:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅很薄还在二月
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.11,0:55:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,和现在不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.26,0:55:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然现在也挺冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.35,0:55:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但那时候更冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.68,0:56:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.31,0:56:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,去那边一下
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.39,0:56:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.43,0:56:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.28,0:56:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.94,0:56:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,离得这么近了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.89,0:56:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不让你说不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.81,0:56:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是强制的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.50,0:56:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微去一下就走
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.86,0:56:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,原点
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.38,0:56:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想看看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.83,0:56:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,时隔数年再会
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.67,0:56:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那是第一次也是最後一次
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.59,0:56:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.59,0:56:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你这相机拍得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.55,0:56:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.05,0:56:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你注意到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.08,0:56:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,当然注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.44,0:57:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.32,0:57:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.35,0:57:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这里充满了回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.83,0:57:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,地点
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.79,0:57:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.51,0:57:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.85,0:57:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.05,0:57:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,心跳得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.07,0:57:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.38,0:57:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,总感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.40,0:57:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.95,0:57:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,自从那次之後就没来了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.93,0:57:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,现在来了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.67,0:58:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.88,0:58:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我又不是在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.49,0:58:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是私人时间
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.94,0:58:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.17,0:58:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是几年前
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.20,0:58:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,4年左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.08,0:58:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,4年前了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.13,0:58:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,四年前和现在的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.65,0:58:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么不同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.91,0:58:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,现在更漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.16,0:58:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,站在这中间
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.67,0:58:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微转过头来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.77,0:58:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那时没有这么从容
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.44,0:58:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,紧张了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.83,0:58:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好像
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.83,0:58:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,被要求摆姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.00,0:58:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.27,0:58:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好像
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.04,0:58:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我紧张得浑身发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.79,0:58:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,终於到了这一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.04,0:59:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,出道作的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.16,0:59:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,时隔四年
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.35,0:59:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,太激动了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.15,0:59:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,超级激动
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.08,0:59:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快乐和辛苦的事各说一个
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.59,0:59:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,作为AV女优
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.63,0:59:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,快乐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.34,0:59:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就是采访活动
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.97,0:59:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,采访
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.13,0:59:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是采访呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.91,0:59:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,青梅竹马进行的采访
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.19,0:59:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快乐的事很多拍了很多相片
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.77,0:59:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有人支援加油给了我鼓励
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.33,1:00:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所以每次工作都会很开心
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.81,1:00:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是最大的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.88,1:00:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.39,1:00:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.48,1:00:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.65,1:00:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没人关注的话
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.62,1:00:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就没办法继续下去了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.56,1:00:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然 平时不会想只会考虑粉丝们
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.50,1:00:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但一个人独处的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.75,1:00:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,或稍微思考的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.40,1:00:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,会很担心能坚持到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.77,1:00:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,感到非常不安
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.14,1:00:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不过会这么想也是因为
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.77,1:01:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我既然做了决心要进入这个世界
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.42,1:01:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就要做到底
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.28,1:01:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常不想後悔
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.42,1:01:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才会对坚持多久感到不安
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.76,1:01:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真是认真啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.69,1:01:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是很认真思考过吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.80,1:01:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,想了超多的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.51,1:01:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但是也有辛苦的地方啦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.92,1:01:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但感觉也得到了回报
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.84,1:01:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我要成为专属演员
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.56,1:01:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,－专属? －专属
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.45,1:01:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,专属是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.02,1:02:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,接了很多厂商的工作发表作品\N现在就固定下来了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.61,1:02:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在决定了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.77,1:02:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在一间公司出就好
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.87,1:02:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就厉害了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.40,1:02:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,超厉害的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.56,1:02:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,－恭喜你 －谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.78,1:02:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.11,1:02:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,－会成为什么 －以後会更厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.68,1:02:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,－很棒喔 －很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.99,1:02:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这是努力的证明啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.39,1:02:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.31,1:02:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.95,1:02:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就算有些痛苦 但是
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.31,1:02:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,只咬想到那是必要的过程
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.10,1:02:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就觉得开心呀
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.03,1:02:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,成了专属演员
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.88,1:02:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,－先恭喜你了 －谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.05,1:02:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,－太好了 －努力了呢这四年里
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.13,1:02:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都在努力着
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.53,1:03:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,－耍哭了 －要哭了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.72,1:03:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,－是啊 －为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.10,1:03:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.28,1:03:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉到自己发生变化吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.45,1:03:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因为成为了专属
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.79,1:03:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.58,1:03:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道是好是坏
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.23,1:03:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是比以前更享受了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.82,1:03:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,和之前一样但也有不同
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.01,1:03:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.64,1:03:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,从这里开始算起的四年前
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.07,1:03:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.30,1:03:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,成了专属後
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.94,1:03:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不是四年前那个我了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.09,1:04:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.09,1:04:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.35,1:04:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.56,1:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可以抱前女友吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.78,1:04:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在这
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.89,1:04:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.84,1:04:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,来拥抱吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.62,1:04:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.62,1:04:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.39,1:04:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那张照片拍到了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.31,1:04:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可能没法再拍一次了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.67,1:04:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别让我尝到这种滋味啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.49,1:04:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,AV女优新井莉玛 做爱
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.53,1:04:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,前女友
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.97,1:04:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要做吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.59,1:04:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.84,1:04:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和A片演员做
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.78,1:04:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因为从来没有嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.82,1:04:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.67,1:04:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.09,1:04:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,－太快了吗? －太快了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.44,1:05:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,今天可不能输给你了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.54,1:05:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗可以吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.76,1:05:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,－可以 －走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.00,1:05:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要上了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.49,1:05:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧去订酒店吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.06,1:05:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要订吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.92,1:05:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,－要 －好快
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.99,1:05:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.87,1:05:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真的订到了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.56,1:05:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这么快
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.70,1:05:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,－很棒吧 －最棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.24,1:05:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,－有男子气概吧 －确实
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.52,1:05:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才去涩谷的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.03,1:05:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,－没感冒吧 －没有吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.17,1:05:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟刚才还兴致勃勃的在说话
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.44,1:05:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,－帅吗 －怎么说呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.35,1:05:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也没听你说这种事
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.34,1:05:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,AV都做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.36,1:05:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.85,1:06:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就说了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.17,1:06:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那种话题不能说的啦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.86,1:06:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真是个好日子呀
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.89,1:06:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,遇到好久没见的人
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.25,1:06:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还做爱了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.61,1:06:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不如说已经结合了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.56,1:06:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,结合
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.62,1:06:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,结台了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.34,1:06:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 都过多少年了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.94,1:06:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,－十年左右了吧 －络於合体了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.45,1:06:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,SM的话是什么属性呢
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.49,1:06:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你来玩弄我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.01,1:06:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.05,1:06:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,技术很厉害吧真的佩服
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.33,1:06:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是两码事
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.38,1:06:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,以结果来说
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.39,1:06:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.97,1:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.50,1:06:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没有绝对的S但有M
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.05,1:07:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.41,1:07:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.61,1:07:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才不就说了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.89,1:07:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了你很多片
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.06,1:07:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.77,1:07:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我的铁粉
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.60,1:07:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.52,1:07:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.13,1:07:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.97,1:07:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说什么
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.77,1:07:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的那个吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.96,1:07:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,AV演员的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.49,1:07:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,性爱技巧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.08,1:07:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.55,1:07:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,满困难的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.50,1:07:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,还没进入状况
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.42,1:07:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就很主动
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.25,1:07:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,骑在上面
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.41,1:08:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是会
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.67,1:08:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那跟我做
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.62,1:08:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.22,1:08:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,又来这套
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.93,1:08:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,临时提要求
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.95,1:08:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,到饭店五分钟内
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.42,1:08:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,才五分钟
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.45,1:08:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,－可以脱吗 －不是在脱了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.44,1:08:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,脱好快啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.08,1:08:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不是之前交往的对象
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.35,1:08:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是女演员
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.52,1:08:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好尴尬
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.67,1:08:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,太尴尬了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.57,1:09:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,－喜欢这样吗 －喜欢
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.87,1:09:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好黑啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.44,1:09:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,脱吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.98,1:09:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头有毛
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.61,1:09:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.72,1:09:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,开心吗
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.96,1:09:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.67,1:09:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这一面啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.89,1:09:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.97,1:09:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.56,1:10:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,－帮我舔 －要舔了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.71,1:11:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.69,1:11:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,亲我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.50,1:11:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,都勃起了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.66,1:11:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.74,1:11:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.74,1:12:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.44,1:13:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,亲我
