Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.79,1:13:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,反过来
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.67,1:13:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,喝下去好乖
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.12,1:13:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.42,1:13:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.83,1:14:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,太热了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.60,1:14:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.85,1:14:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一直看
