Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.62,1:15:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,会挡到
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.91,1:15:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.07,1:15:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.94,1:15:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.53,1:15:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.82,1:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.53,1:15:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要贴紧吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.68,1:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.88,1:15:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.64,1:16:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.23,1:16:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,必须贴上才行
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.75,1:16:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,什么阿
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.93,1:16:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
