Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.31,1:30:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.67,1:30:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了 高潮了高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.42,1:31:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没说呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.83,1:31:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是懂的嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.34,1:31:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.42,1:31:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,－想看插我的地方吧 －想看
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.27,1:31:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害的AV
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.24,1:31:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,AV都这样对吗
