Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.43,1:31:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,－糟糕 －糟糕了?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.70,1:31:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,－没戴套 －还不能射喔
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.79,1:32:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,－我忍耐 －对 还不行
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.12,1:32:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,－很色吗 －很色
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.31,1:32:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.63,1:32:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,倒也是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.46,1:32:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙 太强了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.50,1:32:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,－你太棒了 －很爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.43,1:32:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.81,1:32:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了先停一下
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.26,1:33:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,想射了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.48,1:33:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,－想射 －想射了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.24,1:33:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,－什么 －我想射精
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.35,1:33:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.91,1:33:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那就射吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.76,1:33:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样射
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.54,1:33:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,直接射
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.75,1:33:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我射了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.82,1:33:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要射在哪里
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.57,1:33:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,想射在里面
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.94,1:33:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,射里面啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.74,1:33:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,还不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.08,1:33:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,先让我爽
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.95,1:33:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,－还没吗 －还不行
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.49,1:33:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜欢阿
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.93,1:33:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,－喜欢 －喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.07,1:33:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.43,1:34:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.71,1:34:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.61,1:34:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,－不行了吗 －不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.44,1:34:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.75,1:34:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.77,1:34:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.48,1:34:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快射吧
