Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.36,1:34:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,射出来了?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.17,1:34:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.41,1:34:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,射在里面了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.60,1:34:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,射里面了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.12,1:34:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,想怎么弄
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.35,1:35:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,像AV那样
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.33,1:35:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.52,1:35:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.19,1:35:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.84,1:35:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.41,1:35:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,知道射了很多
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.34,1:35:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.18,1:35:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,－还要吗 －不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.75,1:36:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,才刚射而已
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.16,1:36:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,都射出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.77,1:36:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,说要玩AV的人是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.28,1:36:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你还硬着喔
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.00,1:36:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,－接着在做不行吗 －已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.16,1:36:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能不行麻
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.56,1:36:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,－好爽啊 －好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.23,1:36:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这还是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.76,1:36:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.62,1:36:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是挺好的吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.60,1:36:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次这样吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.55,1:37:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.51,1:37:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好想要
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.58,1:37:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉又硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.46,1:37:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,马上又硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.85,1:37:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.75,1:37:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.32,1:37:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可以动吗
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.86,1:37:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,动快点吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.05,1:38:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好痒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.81,1:38:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,再深一点再深一点
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.98,1:38:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.27,1:38:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,插深一点
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.01,1:38:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒要坏了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.14,1:38:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.06,1:38:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,－快坏掉了 －加油喔
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.85,1:38:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.31,1:38:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.22,1:38:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.62,1:39:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我也不知道在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.75,1:39:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我忍不住要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.51,1:39:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,－要射了 －那边好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.35,1:39:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,－要去了 －要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.30,1:39:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,流出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.89,1:40:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,流下来了快看
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.63,1:40:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,－流出来了 －都流出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.75,1:40:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.98,1:40:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,与其说 这还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.05,1:40:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事情第一次?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.49,1:40:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,－连续的 －但是是你扭的腰
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.75,1:40:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,为了我而扭腰吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.57,1:40:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,为了我而摆动腰部吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.96,1:40:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,空气都进来了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.24,1:40:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.25,1:41:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,被精液弄得一团糟了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.62,1:41:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.23,1:41:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好有精神
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.04,1:41:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还想干你
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.27,1:41:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.93,1:41:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不觉得很爽吗
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.04,1:41:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可以不戴射好几次喔
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.79,1:42:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,很强喔
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.66,1:42:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射的喔
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.10,1:42:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那里很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.62,1:42:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.16,1:42:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.05,1:43:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.40,1:43:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,射哪都可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.75,1:43:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.39,1:43:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,像AV那样射呢\N可以喔
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.11,1:43:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里好呢
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.65,1:43:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就这吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.15,1:43:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.90,1:43:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.39,1:43:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,射到脚了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.90,1:43:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,跟AV一样强阿
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.82,1:43:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.03,1:43:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,都射了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.39,1:43:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.86,1:44:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,－做到了 －做到了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.15,1:44:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,再做点更刺激的事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.07,1:44:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,－什么 －躺下
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.57,1:44:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了 还要吗
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.92,1:44:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还要阿
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.54,1:44:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.73,1:44:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.04,1:44:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.66,1:44:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.71,1:44:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,射了射了射了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.71,1:44:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不要弄\N快停下来 STOP
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.56,1:44:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.37,1:44:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.84,1:44:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.24,1:45:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.13,1:45:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.83,1:45:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是尿喔
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.60,1:45:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.66,1:45:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,潮吹
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.95,1:45:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,潮吹吗
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.89,1:45:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,喷了好多
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.80,1:45:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就像AV那样
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.93,1:45:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.62,1:45:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,超级舒服的
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.67,1:45:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊各种意义上
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.05,1:45:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.20,1:45:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.78,1:45:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.65,1:45:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,成人片
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.08,1:45:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,AV演员的我
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.29,1:45:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,干得爽吧
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.13,1:45:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,己经不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.99,1:45:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.42,1:45:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.40,1:45:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.29,1:46:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,家里很远吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.27,1:46:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.70,1:46:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不怕吗
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.40,1:46:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有点怕 还有一小时
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.86,1:46:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要过夜吗
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.45,1:46:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.58,1:46:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,－过夜 －可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.38,1:46:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,明天也没有工作
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.43,1:46:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是作为交换 要干到脚软喔
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.93,1:46:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,－要干到死吗 －能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.93,1:46:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗 那就来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.18,1:46:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,先去洗个澡在浴室做爱吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.99,1:46:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在浴室里做完之後
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.26,1:46:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,再做到早上
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.15,1:46:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,前女友和前男友一起
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.41,1:47:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,－一直做到早上 －对
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.10,1:47:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有睡好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.52,1:47:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有睡好
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.03,1:47:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有点色色的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.92,1:47:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是昨天的余韵吗
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.80,1:47:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,还残留着
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.61,1:47:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,－要喝水吗 －想喝
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.08,1:47:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,常温的水还是冰水
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.29,1:47:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,常温
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.04,1:48:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,－旱上的你是私人时间\N－别说了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.90,1:48:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,私人时间
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.98,1:48:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,赏然是私人时间 还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.16,1:48:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要准备了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.57,1:48:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.60,1:48:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,－亲一下 －好喔
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.99,1:49:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,牙膏自己弄
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.03,1:49:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是耍你刷
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.40,1:49:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己来
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.59,1:49:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,自己能行的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.33,1:49:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.26,1:49:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上突然想到一件事
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.07,1:49:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,睡醒感觉挺不错的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.87,1:50:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有种没有睡醒的真实感
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.53,1:50:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个朋友说你睡相很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.21,1:50:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,早上是我会怕吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.46,1:50:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,会怕?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.83,1:50:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔 很可怕喔
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.66,1:51:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,还没刷好
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.72,1:51:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.17,1:51:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好羞耻
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.54,1:51:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,快要退房了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.71,1:51:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可能连一小时都不到吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.81,1:51:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,换衣服
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.66,1:51:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,再化个妆
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.86,1:51:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微打理一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.92,1:51:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,应该不会花多少时间吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.77,1:51:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,交往的时\N没想过会在东京这样
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.69,1:52:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.88,1:52:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.53,1:52:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,因为一直很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.98,1:52:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,所以反而一下子就醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.27,1:52:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.81,1:52:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.82,1:52:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,自己变成大人了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:17.11,1:52:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.45,1:52:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,已经件不到了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:52:29.41,1:52:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,－不想见我了吗 －什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:36.53,1:52:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们又见面了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.61,1:52:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,－很想见我吧 －很想见
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.67,1:52:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.72,1:53:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不同世界的人不会再见了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.87,1:53:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.04,1:53:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.88,1:53:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可以讲一件奇怪的事吗
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.53,1:53:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.44,1:53:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.68,1:53:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.54,1:53:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.98,1:54:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我说跟我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.59,1:54:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,会不拍成人片吗
Dialogue: 0,1:54:05.35,1:54:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是开玩笑哦
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.60,1:54:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.30,1:54:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你是认真的
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.41,1:54:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不想让我拍吗
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.80,1:54:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.01,1:54:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能陪我
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.50,1:54:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大概不会停拍
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.41,1:54:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,与其说是大概
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.30,1:54:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不会停拍的
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.48,1:54:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你笑什么
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.45,1:54:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,用亲亲混过去
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.06,1:54:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,混什么
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.39,1:54:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,想糊弄过去啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.29,1:55:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,工作不会辞掉的
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.56,1:55:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,被甩掉了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.17,1:55:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我没说甩掉你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.40,1:55:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,时间不早了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.57,1:55:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,请稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.28,1:55:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,想做
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.37,1:55:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,想做 这可能是最後一次机会了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.87,1:56:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没打算甩你呢
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.19,1:56:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次吗
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.81,1:56:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 我会把你榨乾的
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.65,1:56:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,－又流出来了 －有点害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,1:56:52.14,1:56:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,想要吗
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.55,1:56:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,－什么啦 －不要吗
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.51,1:59:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:59:20.50,1:59:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好色喔
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.40,1:59:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,－我想做爱 －想做爱吗
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.86,1:59:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,－真好笑 －我想做嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.21,1:59:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,2:01:01.30,2:01:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不得了
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.97,2:01:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,－感觉真棒 －很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.13,2:01:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.30,2:01:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,－真想一直做 －一直吗
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.54,2:01:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不是一直在做吗
Dialogue: 0,2:01:22.59,2:01:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:01:39.27,2:01:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快不行了
Dialogue: 0,2:01:50.30,2:01:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.94,2:02:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,去了去了去了
Dialogue: 0,2:02:33.41,2:02:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,－做到退房房 －做到底吗
Dialogue: 0,2:02:35.79,2:02:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我想一直做到极限为止
Dialogue: 0,2:02:38.02,2:02:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那就做到极限为止
Dialogue: 0,2:03:23.90,2:03:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,2:03:25.49,2:03:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:03:28.30,2:03:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:03:29.09,2:03:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,2:03:29.89,2:03:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我
Dialogue: 0,2:03:32.24,2:03:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:03:37.65,2:03:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,－忍一下 一起高潮吧\N－再忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.32,2:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:48.08,2:03:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,－爽到忍不住了\N－那么爽啊
Dialogue: 0,2:03:53.88,2:03:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,射你里面一直到最後
Dialogue: 0,2:03:56.27,2:03:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那就射到极限吧
Dialogue: 0,2:03:58.18,2:03:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,能射多少就射多少
Dialogue: 0,2:04:00.85,2:04:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟己经没有了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:04:02.75,2:04:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:04:13.15,2:04:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,爽死了
Dialogue: 0,2:04:15.97,2:04:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,2:04:17.17,2:04:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一起高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,2:04:18.14,2:04:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一起吧
Dialogue: 0,2:04:59.70,2:05:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,喷出来好多
Dialogue: 0,2:05:04.70,2:05:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙阿
Dialogue: 0,2:05:08.43,2:05:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙阿
Dialogue: 0,2:05:12.70,2:05:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,－浑身都是 －都这样了还说什么
Dialogue: 0,2:05:17.56,2:05:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,干大久了
Dialogue: 0,2:05:22.13,2:05:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,脚软了
Dialogue: 0,2:05:23.39,2:05:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,流出来了
Dialogue: 0,2:05:24.70,2:05:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,2:05:39.73,2:05:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,还行吗
Dialogue: 0,2:05:43.80,2:05:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还可以吗
Dialogue: 0,2:06:08.71,2:06:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:06:24.68,2:06:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,滴下来了
Dialogue: 0,2:06:26.47,2:06:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,滴下来了
Dialogue: 0,2:06:27.67,2:06:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样插吧
Dialogue: 0,2:06:29.42,2:06:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样插进来吧
Dialogue: 0,2:06:30.31,2:06:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,2:06:32.55,2:06:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:36.09,2:06:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了喔
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.96,2:06:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,2:06:46.85,2:06:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,2:06:51.07,2:06:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了才说
Dialogue: 0,2:06:53.50,2:06:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,2:06:55.92,2:06:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,2:07:28.89,2:07:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,2:07:33.26,2:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因为不想忘记这个味道
Dialogue: 0,2:07:43.04,2:07:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这样做之後 就跟别人做不了了喔
Dialogue: 0,2:07:45.64,2:07:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,－不做 －不做?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:48.38,2:07:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,2:08:07.74,2:08:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,2:08:23.80,2:08:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,去了去了
Dialogue: 0,2:08:35.85,2:08:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,亲一下
Dialogue: 0,2:08:44.25,2:08:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:47.00,2:08:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,想吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:55.14,2:09:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟之前交往的男朋友 排名第几
Dialogue: 0,2:09:00.43,2:09:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,排第几?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:03.99,2:09:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没有这样比较过 试着比看看
Dialogue: 0,2:09:09.59,2:09:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.61,2:09:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,前女友最棒了
Dialogue: 0,2:09:14.41,2:09:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,前女友最棒了
Dialogue: 0,2:09:17.17,2:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,最棒的吗
Dialogue: 0,2:09:18.63,2:09:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那是当然啊
Dialogue: 0,2:09:20.07,2:09:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,2:09:21.54,2:09:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.01,2:09:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.66,2:10:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉要流出来了
Dialogue: 0,2:10:03.34,2:10:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,流出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,2:10:04.97,2:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,射给我吧
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.46,2:10:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你骑上来
Dialogue: 0,2:10:22.04,2:10:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,2:10:23.53,2:10:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,2:10:51.31,2:10:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,2:11:01.46,2:11:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这样比较好吗
Dialogue: 0,2:11:05.00,2:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够吗
Dialogue: 0,2:11:06.00,2:11:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,2:11:09.21,2:11:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我要记住
Dialogue: 0,2:11:11.32,2:11:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,会坏掉的
Dialogue: 0,2:11:12.61,2:11:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,坏掉
Dialogue: 0,2:11:13.84,2:11:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一起坏掉吧
Dialogue: 0,2:11:14.94,2:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一起坏掉
Dialogue: 0,2:11:18.77,2:11:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,2:11:20.95,2:11:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:11:25.06,2:11:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,快高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:11:26.34,2:11:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:11:27.33,2:11:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,2:12:22.63,2:12:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,2:12:23.41,2:12:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,2:12:31.07,2:12:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,射了好多
Dialogue: 0,2:12:33.03,2:12:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真的会射出来哦
Dialogue: 0,2:12:44.97,2:12:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,2:12:47.00,2:12:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,－我可以伸进去吗 －可以喔
Dialogue: 0,2:13:01.88,2:13:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好色喔
Dialogue: 0,2:13:04.30,2:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你舔舔看
Dialogue: 0,2:13:11.40,2:13:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好浓厚
Dialogue: 0,2:13:16.43,2:13:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 不开玩笑 我们的关系真的很好
Dialogue: 0,2:13:20.76,2:13:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧 己经搞不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,2:13:32.31,2:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌吗
Dialogue: 0,2:13:36.55,2:13:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要是讨厌的话 我就不舔了
Dialogue: 0,2:14:21.95,2:14:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有精子的味道
Dialogue: 0,2:14:42.00,2:14:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,2:14:46.91,2:14:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想辞职
Dialogue: 0,2:14:54.06,2:14:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,2:14:56.50,2:14:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,再做一次
Dialogue: 0,2:15:02.43,2:15:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,干好几次了
Dialogue: 0,2:15:12.41,2:15:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还没说是最後呢
Dialogue: 0,2:16:11.81,2:16:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,－好色喔 －真舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:16:34.90,2:16:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:16:41.32,2:16:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了 我要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:16:49.64,2:16:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:17:19.38,2:17:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,－小穴湿透了 －真不得了
Dialogue: 0,2:17:27.12,2:17:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得可以
Dialogue: 0,2:17:42.79,2:17:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,－好舒服 －好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,2:17:47.63,2:17:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谁呢
Dialogue: 0,2:17:50.90,2:17:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,－说谁呢 －我说你
Dialogue: 0,2:18:01.70,2:18:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,－我也喜欢你\N－肉棒变大了
Dialogue: 0,2:18:10.22,2:18:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,2:18:12.91,2:18:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,2:18:13.96,2:18:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,2:18:17.00,2:18:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,之前没说过
Dialogue: 0,2:18:18.99,2:18:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,眼神没说
Dialogue: 0,2:18:20.54,2:18:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,已经说了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:18:22.05,2:18:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,快动起来
Dialogue: 0,2:18:24.01,2:18:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,2:18:25.27,2:18:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不够的
Dialogue: 0,2:18:43.30,2:18:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙阿
Dialogue: 0,2:19:37.20,2:19:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,－可以更激烈吗 －可以喔
Dialogue: 0,2:19:42.32,2:19:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:19:47.12,2:19:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,2:19:53.67,2:19:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这个
Dialogue: 0,2:20:02.63,2:20:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:20:15.06,2:20:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了吗 可以喔射给我
Dialogue: 0,2:20:47.29,2:20:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,2:20:49.50,2:20:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这边吗
Dialogue: 0,2:20:58.53,2:20:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,2:20:59.75,2:21:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,已经口齿不清了 看到这个的时候
Dialogue: 0,2:21:10.12,2:21:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射在里面吗 再一次的
Dialogue: 0,2:21:15.70,2:21:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,2:21:19.83,2:21:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你射在里面吧
Dialogue: 0,2:21:28.34,2:21:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,私底下说射在里面了
Dialogue: 0,2:21:33.50,2:21:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:21:51.16,2:21:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,2:21:53.78,2:21:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,－拜托你一件是 －什么?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:55.43,2:21:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,张开眼睛
Dialogue: 0,2:21:56.59,2:21:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,2:22:01.17,2:22:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:22:03.81,2:22:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,2:22:05.74,2:22:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,去了去了
Dialogue: 0,2:22:07.97,2:22:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,2:22:39.48,2:22:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,－这下糟糕了 －好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,2:22:43.52,2:22:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来互相说喜欢
Dialogue: 0,2:22:45.93,2:22:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还要说啊
Dialogue: 0,2:22:47.36,2:22:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,－喜欢 －喜欢
Dialogue: 0,2:23:29.25,2:23:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你摸摸看屁眼
Dialogue: 0,2:23:46.83,2:23:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你射出来好多喔
Dialogue: 0,2:23:51.38,2:23:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那就说不要嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:23:57.14,2:23:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我把肉棒舔乾净
Dialogue: 0,2:24:08.93,2:24:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,都是精液的味道
Dialogue: 0,2:24:13.17,2:24:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,滑溜溜的
Dialogue: 0,2:24:23.71,2:24:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒还很硬呢
Dialogue: 0,2:24:26.14,2:24:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要继续
Dialogue: 0,2:24:30.21,2:24:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要继续吗
Dialogue: 0,2:24:32.46,2:24:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 来吧
Dialogue: 0,2:25:05.83,2:25:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉真舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:25:14.87,2:25:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见超级开心的
Dialogue: 0,2:25:17.75,2:25:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,2:25:20.23,2:25:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然会寂寞
Dialogue: 0,2:25:22.02,2:25:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,2:25:24.29,2:25:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这是最後一次
Dialogue: 0,2:25:25.98,2:25:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要说是最後
Dialogue: 0,2:25:28.67,2:25:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好想念
Dialogue: 0,2:25:30.88,2:25:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,2:25:33.22,2:25:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那你是一号粉丝
Dialogue: 0,2:25:36.54,2:25:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我要当零号
Dialogue: 0,2:25:39.05,2:25:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,零号就是
Dialogue: 0,2:25:46.79,2:25:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没有号码
Dialogue: 0,2:25:47.87,2:25:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,特别的
Dialogue: 0,2:25:49.77,2:25:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,2:26:15.20,2:26:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,2:26:22.19,2:26:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,2:26:25.48,2:26:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:26:28.17,2:26:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,2:26:32.07,2:26:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮吧
Dialogue: 0,2:26:42.63,2:26:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可以弄脏你吗
Dialogue: 0,2:26:44.58,2:26:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,2:26:45.15,2:26:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,用精液弄脏行吗
Dialogue: 0,2:26:46.01,2:26:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情地弄脏吧
Dialogue: 0,2:26:47.36,2:26:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,射到你脏掉
Dialogue: 0,2:26:50.51,2:26:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,2:27:08.37,2:27:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,被做标记了
Dialogue: 0,2:27:32.81,2:27:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我想在里里外外留下痕迹
Dialogue: 0,2:27:42.44,2:27:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你一边笑还一边做啊
Dialogue: 0,2:28:01.23,2:28:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,2:28:07.36,2:28:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能不可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,2:28:09.46,2:28:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你连续干了两天
Dialogue: 0,2:28:16.17,2:28:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真是值得自蒙的经历
Dialogue: 0,2:28:17.88,2:28:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,超级值得炫惧的啊
Dialogue: 0,2:28:21.65,2:28:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,时间没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,2:28:24.35,2:28:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,2:28:29.88,2:28:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,超级不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,2:28:31.13,2:28:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,与其说是不妙不如说超过了
Dialogue: 0,2:28:33.49,2:28:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,超过了
Dialogue: 0,2:28:36.23,2:28:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要快点
Dialogue: 0,2:28:37.93,2:28:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,快速换衣服
Dialogue: 0,2:28:39.31,2:28:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以
Dialogue: 0,2:28:41.76,2:28:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这二天超棒啊
Dialogue: 0,2:28:44.61,2:28:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,－开心吗
Dialogue: 0,2:28:45.60,2:28:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,很开心还是喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,2:28:50.10,2:28:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这份心情是不会变的
Dialogue: 0,2:28:52.44,2:28:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,2:28:54.03,2:28:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那就一直喜欢下去吧
Dialogue: 0,2:29:05.67,2:29:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我会努力当专属演员
Dialogue: 0,2:29:08.75,2:29:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我支持你哦
Dialogue: 0,2:29:10.24,2:29:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,2:29:13.44,2:29:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那你全买了
Dialogue: 0,2:29:14.98,2:29:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我全买了虽然我不太懂是什么
Dialogue: 0,2:29:20.86,2:29:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可能还有很多事
Dialogue: 0,2:29:22.61,2:29:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,2:29:23.37,2:29:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,2:29:24.70,2:29:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,2:29:26.35,2:29:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你是最好的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,2:29:28.80,2:29:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一直看着你呢
Dialogue: 0,2:29:33.98,2:29:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,2:29:36.35,2:29:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,最後
Dialogue: 0,2:29:37.35,2:29:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,抱一下
Dialogue: 0,2:29:40.07,2:29:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很愉快哦
Dialogue: 0,2:29:44.06,2:29:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,2:29:45.39,2:29:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,2:29:50.20,2:29:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,换衣服了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:29:51.13,2:29:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一起换吧
Dialogue: 0,2:29:52.17,2:29:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,换衣服
